WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:18.634 align:middle line:10%
[THEME MUSIC]

00:00:18.634 --> 00:00:21.300 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA MEREDITH: You've likely
already seen my first interview

00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:23.450 align:middle line:84%
with Susan Lindauer,
in which we talked

00:00:23.450 --> 00:00:25.970 align:middle line:84%
about how she was
identified as an Iraqi agent

00:00:25.970 --> 00:00:28.280 align:middle line:84%
and put in federal
prison without a trial.

00:00:28.280 --> 00:00:31.730 align:middle line:10%
In fact, she was working as
a CIA asset on the ground,

00:00:31.730 --> 00:00:34.530 align:middle line:10%
giving advance warning
of 9/11 and negotiating

00:00:34.530 --> 00:00:36.990 align:middle line:10%
for peaceful
relationships with Iraq.

00:00:36.990 --> 00:00:38.880 align:middle line:10%
We continue our
discussion now focusing

00:00:38.880 --> 00:00:41.510 align:middle line:10%
on what happened when she
was taken into custody,

00:00:41.510 --> 00:00:43.570 align:middle line:10%
powerless in the
hands of psychiatrists

00:00:43.570 --> 00:00:45.680 align:middle line:10%
colluding with
the US government.

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:48.180 align:middle line:84%
To keep her quiet regarding
her findings of pre-

00:00:48.180 --> 00:00:50.600 align:middle line:84%
and post 9/11 events
in the Middle East,

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:53.740 align:middle line:84%
she had to be found
incompetent to stand trial.

00:00:53.740 --> 00:00:57.500 align:middle line:84%
This is where her fight for
her life and her mind began.

00:00:57.500 --> 00:00:59.490 align:middle line:90%
And I welcome you back Susan.

00:00:59.490 --> 00:01:00.840 align:middle line:90%
What an incredible story.

00:01:00.840 --> 00:01:03.190 align:middle line:84%
By now, I think people are
familiar with the first part

00:01:03.190 --> 00:01:04.129 align:middle line:90%
of the story.

00:01:04.129 --> 00:01:06.840 align:middle line:84%
But one thing we didn't
go into there as they're

00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:08.920 align:middle line:84%
trying to prove
that you're crazy,

00:01:08.920 --> 00:01:10.650 align:middle line:84%
was the fact that you
were alerting them

00:01:10.650 --> 00:01:12.570 align:middle line:84%
to events that were
going to be coming down,

00:01:12.570 --> 00:01:16.310 align:middle line:84%
this was in August of
2001 in lower Manhattan,

00:01:16.310 --> 00:01:19.100 align:middle line:84%
involving airplanes, and
specifically the World Trade

00:01:19.100 --> 00:01:19.620 align:middle line:90%
Center.

00:01:19.620 --> 00:01:21.310 align:middle line:84%
You can't get more
specific than that.

00:01:21.310 --> 00:01:23.716 align:middle line:84%
And as I was reading
about your story

00:01:23.716 --> 00:01:26.340 align:middle line:84%
and reading in the book what you
were specifically warning them

00:01:26.340 --> 00:01:30.830 align:middle line:84%
of, I was reminded of a document
that came across shortly

00:01:30.830 --> 00:01:33.330 align:middle line:90%
after 9/11.

00:01:33.330 --> 00:01:34.840 align:middle line:84%
It was regarding
David Shippers, who

00:01:34.840 --> 00:01:37.460 align:middle line:84%
was the lead counsel who
was leading the impeachment

00:01:37.460 --> 00:01:40.710 align:middle line:84%
proceedings against
Clinton, right?

00:01:40.710 --> 00:01:43.330 align:middle line:84%
He had been approached by FBI
agents, and I have it all here.

00:01:43.330 --> 00:01:45.320 align:middle line:84%
I went back into my old
files and found this.

00:01:45.320 --> 00:01:48.330 align:middle line:84%
I printed it out on
November 11, 2001,

00:01:48.330 --> 00:01:50.460 align:middle line:84%
so it originated
sometime before that.

00:01:50.460 --> 00:01:53.480 align:middle line:84%
Essentially, FBI agents had
come to him for legal protection

00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:58.510 align:middle line:84%
because they were telling the
managers of the departments

00:01:58.510 --> 00:02:01.390 align:middle line:84%
above them, I don't know the
vernacular for their industry,

00:02:01.390 --> 00:02:04.080 align:middle line:84%
that these events
were coming down also.

00:02:04.080 --> 00:02:07.010 align:middle line:84%
Each one of them was saying,
instead of listening,

00:02:07.010 --> 00:02:08.960 align:middle line:84%
they were being put
on leaves of absence.

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:10.714 align:middle line:90%
Some were even being fired.

00:02:10.714 --> 00:02:12.130 align:middle line:84%
So they came to
him for protection

00:02:12.130 --> 00:02:14.380 align:middle line:84%
because they had to break
their national security oath

00:02:14.380 --> 00:02:16.090 align:middle line:90%
to divulge this information.

00:02:16.090 --> 00:02:18.730 align:middle line:84%
And now, this is a
high-profile individual

00:02:18.730 --> 00:02:19.710 align:middle line:90%
who tried to go public.

00:02:19.710 --> 00:02:22.320 align:middle line:84%
He even went on the
"Alex Jones Show."

00:02:22.320 --> 00:02:25.010 align:middle line:84%
This is when you were
doing the same thing

00:02:25.010 --> 00:02:26.740 align:middle line:90%
on the inside channels.

00:02:26.740 --> 00:02:30.450 align:middle line:84%
Shippers went so far as to
go on the "Alex Jones Show"

00:02:30.450 --> 00:02:31.542 align:middle line:90%
and talk about this.

00:02:31.542 --> 00:02:33.875 align:middle line:84%
Now, no one has probably heard
his name, a lot of people

00:02:33.875 --> 00:02:35.460 align:middle line:90%
have never heard your name.

00:02:35.460 --> 00:02:36.085 align:middle line:90%
He disappeared.

00:02:36.085 --> 00:02:38.459 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I don't know where he
is now and what he's doing,

00:02:38.459 --> 00:02:39.826 align:middle line:90%
but you don't find much on him.

00:02:39.826 --> 00:02:40.700 align:middle line:90%
>>SUSAN LINDAUER: No.

00:02:40.700 --> 00:02:40.920 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So he was--

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:42.540 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: Most
people go into hiding

00:02:42.540 --> 00:02:43.290 align:middle line:90%
after these sorts of things.

00:02:43.290 --> 00:02:45.430 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: What happens-- now, he
went on the "Alex Jones Show,"

00:02:45.430 --> 00:02:46.638 align:middle line:90%
we know what happened to you.

00:02:46.638 --> 00:02:48.780 align:middle line:84%
What is the common
scenario if someone chooses

00:02:48.780 --> 00:02:51.310 align:middle line:84%
to speak when the government
does not want them

00:02:51.310 --> 00:02:53.430 align:middle line:84%
to-- what would have
happened theoretically

00:02:53.430 --> 00:02:54.180 align:middle line:90%
to him and others?

00:02:54.180 --> 00:02:55.304 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: They are fired.

00:02:55.304 --> 00:02:59.600 align:middle line:10%
They are blacklisted so
they cannot get other work.

00:02:59.600 --> 00:03:07.050 align:middle line:10%
In my case, my CIA handler
was paid off $13 million.

00:03:07.050 --> 00:03:10.360 align:middle line:84%
And he was paid off from
money for the emergency

00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:12.160 align:middle line:84%
appropriations for the
9/11 investigation.

00:03:12.160 --> 00:03:14.080 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: Wait, to deny you?

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:16.635 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: To forget
the 9/11 story.

00:03:16.635 --> 00:03:18.410 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Oh, to
forget the 9/11 story.

00:03:18.410 --> 00:03:18.620 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:03:18.620 --> 00:03:18.820 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: Yes.

00:03:18.820 --> 00:03:19.670 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Because he
had knowledge too.

00:03:19.670 --> 00:03:21.169 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: And
then I was arrested.

00:03:21.169 --> 00:03:24.000 align:middle line:84%
And after my arrest, he
refused to acknowledge

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:26.644 align:middle line:84%
that he'd worked with
me for nine years.

00:03:26.644 --> 00:03:27.310 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:03:27.310 --> 00:03:29.240 align:middle line:84%
I just wanted to set
this up because we

00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:30.630 align:middle line:90%
didn't get to that part.

00:03:30.630 --> 00:03:32.930 align:middle line:84%
And the reason we're not
focusing a lot on 9/11

00:03:32.930 --> 00:03:34.670 align:middle line:84%
is because it's
been done to death.

00:03:34.670 --> 00:03:37.260 align:middle line:84%
If anyone doesn't know by
now that it was an inside job

00:03:37.260 --> 00:03:39.720 align:middle line:84%
and that they at least expected
it and had full advance

00:03:39.720 --> 00:03:42.860 align:middle line:84%
knowledge, then there are
plenty of books out there.

00:03:42.860 --> 00:03:44.490 align:middle line:90%
So we're going to continue on.

00:03:44.490 --> 00:03:47.034 align:middle line:84%
I just wanted to validate
that with this too.

00:03:47.034 --> 00:03:48.950 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: It's really
important because what

00:03:48.950 --> 00:03:54.687 align:middle line:84%
happened to me regarding
9/11 and the cover up we're

00:03:54.687 --> 00:03:55.770 align:middle line:90%
going to talk today about.

00:03:55.770 --> 00:03:57.895 align:middle line:84%
Everything we're talking
about the cover up of Iraq

00:03:57.895 --> 00:03:59.542 align:middle line:84%
also applies to the
cover up of 9/11.

00:03:59.542 --> 00:04:00.500 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, exactly.

00:04:00.500 --> 00:04:02.800 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: And it
especially applies to 9/11

00:04:02.800 --> 00:04:06.870 align:middle line:84%
because the judge in my
case, Michael Mukasey,

00:04:06.870 --> 00:04:10.990 align:middle line:84%
was also hearing the insurance
claims for Larry Silverstein.

00:04:10.990 --> 00:04:11.740 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Oh, yes.

00:04:11.740 --> 00:04:16.420 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: And the $7 billion
payout that Larry Silverstein

00:04:16.420 --> 00:04:18.233 align:middle line:84%
was demanding from the
insurance companies.

00:04:18.233 --> 00:04:18.899 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:04:18.899 --> 00:04:21.540 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: My attorneys
used to cross paths

00:04:21.540 --> 00:04:24.490 align:middle line:84%
with his attorneys
in the courthouse.

00:04:24.490 --> 00:04:28.330 align:middle line:84%
And there were times when I was
brought in shackles in front

00:04:28.330 --> 00:04:31.680 align:middle line:84%
of Judge Mukasey and Larry
Silverstein's attorneys

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:32.600 align:middle line:90%
would be there.

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:36.160 align:middle line:84%
And I would say, your
honor, we knew about 9/11.

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:40.820 align:middle line:90%
Please, I beg you for hearing.

00:04:40.820 --> 00:04:43.280 align:middle line:90%
I beg you to hear my witnesses.

00:04:43.280 --> 00:04:45.890 align:middle line:90%
Let my witnesses confront them.

00:04:45.890 --> 00:04:49.860 align:middle line:84%
Ask them any questions you
want, but let me testify.

00:04:49.860 --> 00:04:51.960 align:middle line:90%
Let me prove this to you.

00:04:51.960 --> 00:04:56.630 align:middle line:84%
And it was a
terrifying experience

00:04:56.630 --> 00:04:59.430 align:middle line:90%
and it was baffling to me.

00:04:59.430 --> 00:05:02.920 align:middle line:84%
I was bewildered that
the government could

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:07.580 align:middle line:84%
lie about our 9/11 warnings
and then turn around and say

00:05:07.580 --> 00:05:12.040 align:middle line:84%
that I was incompetent, though I
gave advance warnings to the US

00:05:12.040 --> 00:05:13.474 align:middle line:90%
Attorney General John Ashcroft.

00:05:13.474 --> 00:05:14.140 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:05:14.140 --> 00:05:17.500 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: And I had
requested, in August of 2001,

00:05:17.500 --> 00:05:21.760 align:middle line:84%
an emergency broadcast alert
across all federal agencies.

00:05:21.760 --> 00:05:27.080 align:middle line:84%
So it was my notification
that put the FBI on alert.

00:05:27.080 --> 00:05:29.500 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, and
also Shippers, he

00:05:29.500 --> 00:05:32.550 align:middle line:84%
had repeated phone calls
in to John Ashcroft,

00:05:32.550 --> 00:05:34.250 align:middle line:84%
and he was operating
at a high level.

00:05:34.250 --> 00:05:35.450 align:middle line:90%
He refused the phone calls.

00:05:35.450 --> 00:05:39.134 align:middle line:84%
Telling him what it was about,
Ashcroft's office and Ashcroft

00:05:39.134 --> 00:05:41.425 align:middle line:84%
would not accept those phone
calls and the information.

00:05:41.425 --> 00:05:45.250 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: Ashcroft
was a despicable coward

00:05:45.250 --> 00:05:46.334 align:middle line:90%
as far as I was concerned.

00:05:46.334 --> 00:05:48.374 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I think that
the record will show that.

00:05:48.374 --> 00:05:48.970 align:middle line:90%
So now--

00:05:48.970 --> 00:05:52.372 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: He was a coward, and
he failed America very badly.

00:05:52.372 --> 00:05:54.205 align:middle line:84%
And the only thing worse
than being a coward

00:05:54.205 --> 00:05:57.920 align:middle line:84%
is to blame somebody else for
your own mistakes to the point

00:05:57.920 --> 00:06:00.575 align:middle line:84%
that you arrest them and
throw them in prison.

00:06:00.575 --> 00:06:01.950 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That
makes you a coward

00:06:01.950 --> 00:06:03.134 align:middle line:90%
and a criminal in my book.

00:06:03.134 --> 00:06:03.800 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: Yes.

00:06:03.800 --> 00:06:06.644 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: OK, so lets talk
about the crime aspect of this.

00:06:06.644 --> 00:06:08.310 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: So, the
crime aspect of this

00:06:08.310 --> 00:06:10.720 align:middle line:90%
was that I was arrested.

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:16.290 align:middle line:84%
And first, I was on bail for
$500,000, which is insulting.

00:06:16.290 --> 00:06:21.640 align:middle line:84%
I had to deal with the insult
and the discrediting of being

00:06:21.640 --> 00:06:25.980 align:middle line:84%
labeled sort of a psych
case from day one.

00:06:25.980 --> 00:06:28.687 align:middle line:84%
And they said, why did
they do that to you?

00:06:28.687 --> 00:06:30.020 align:middle line:90%
And I was like, are you kidding?

00:06:30.020 --> 00:06:31.800 align:middle line:90%
Why did they not do it to me?

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:33.634 align:middle line:84%
Of course, they have
to try to discredit me.

00:06:33.634 --> 00:06:36.174 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You were getting the
political implications by now.

00:06:36.174 --> 00:06:38.120 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: Anybody,
anybody could understand

00:06:38.120 --> 00:06:39.870 align:middle line:84%
the political implications
if they thought

00:06:39.870 --> 00:06:42.610 align:middle line:84%
about it for more
than five seconds.

00:06:42.610 --> 00:06:48.430 align:middle line:84%
It was a ludicrous argument that
I was this psychiatric case.

00:06:48.430 --> 00:06:52.240 align:middle line:84%
And the papers themselves
never showed evidence

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:55.670 align:middle line:84%
of psychiatric dysfunction
on my part, what they said

00:06:55.670 --> 00:07:01.660 align:middle line:84%
was that I was 95%
convinced of my innocence.

00:07:01.660 --> 00:07:04.100 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, I
could not appreciate

00:07:04.100 --> 00:07:07.330 align:middle line:84%
the gravity of the
charges against me.

00:07:07.330 --> 00:07:11.150 align:middle line:84%
And so long as I continued
to demand a hearing,

00:07:11.150 --> 00:07:14.940 align:middle line:84%
demand the right to disprove
the allegations against me

00:07:14.940 --> 00:07:18.420 align:middle line:84%
and to show that I had
not broken the law,

00:07:18.420 --> 00:07:22.920 align:middle line:84%
that in itself qualified
as a mental defect, which

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:26.140 align:middle line:84%
rendered me incapable
of standing for trial.

00:07:26.140 --> 00:07:28.490 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Delusional and
delusions of grandeur.

00:07:28.490 --> 00:07:30.300 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: Yes, grandiosity.

00:07:30.300 --> 00:07:37.070 align:middle line:84%
Which is what Soviet psychiatry
used throughout the Brezhnev

00:07:37.070 --> 00:07:41.550 align:middle line:84%
and air age and Stalin,
right up through Gorbachev.

00:07:41.550 --> 00:07:47.890 align:middle line:84%
People forget that in the Soviet
Union, 30% of all activists

00:07:47.890 --> 00:07:51.260 align:middle line:84%
were targeted under
Soviet psychiatry.

00:07:51.260 --> 00:07:53.845 align:middle line:84%
They were accused of what they
called sluggish schizophrenia.

00:07:53.845 --> 00:07:56.970 align:middle line:90%


00:07:56.970 --> 00:08:00.890 align:middle line:84%
These were reformers, and so
they had delusions of reform,

00:08:00.890 --> 00:08:04.680 align:middle line:84%
delusions of persecution,
delusions of paranoia.

00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:06.150 align:middle line:84%
The belief that
you could actually

00:08:06.150 --> 00:08:08.950 align:middle line:84%
make a difference
and change society,

00:08:08.950 --> 00:08:13.840 align:middle line:84%
and the Soviet psychiatrist
mirroring my situation exactly,

00:08:13.840 --> 00:08:17.570 align:middle line:84%
the same vocabulary,
that the individual

00:08:17.570 --> 00:08:21.450 align:middle line:84%
would show no outward symptoms
of mental illness other

00:08:21.450 --> 00:08:24.040 align:middle line:90%
than mild neuroses.

00:08:24.040 --> 00:08:24.850 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:08:24.850 --> 00:08:28.830 align:middle line:84%
There would be no behavioral
issues in society,

00:08:28.830 --> 00:08:32.500 align:middle line:84%
but the fact that you
opposed the government, what

00:08:32.500 --> 00:08:37.860 align:middle line:84%
we call in the West
oppositional defiance disorder.

00:08:37.860 --> 00:08:39.044 align:middle line:90%
I was accused of this.

00:08:39.044 --> 00:08:41.210 align:middle line:84%
I was accused of this and
I was like, oh, thank you.

00:08:41.210 --> 00:08:41.793 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: ODD.

00:08:41.793 --> 00:08:43.026 align:middle line:90%
There must be a pill for it.

00:08:43.026 --> 00:08:44.150 align:middle line:90%
We're going to get to that.

00:08:44.150 --> 00:08:44.680 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: We're
going to get to that.

00:08:44.680 --> 00:08:46.280 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: They have really
strong pills for that one.

00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:48.363 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: They have
really strong pills for that

00:08:48.363 --> 00:08:50.120 align:middle line:84%
and they are scary
pills, I'll tell you.

00:08:50.120 --> 00:08:50.870 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Oh, God.

00:08:50.870 --> 00:08:53.940 align:middle line:84%
OK, before we get to the pill
part, let's talk about you

00:08:53.940 --> 00:08:55.520 align:middle line:90%
end up in court.

00:08:55.520 --> 00:08:58.300 align:middle line:84%
Now because this falls
under the Patriot Act,

00:08:58.300 --> 00:09:01.480 align:middle line:84%
you have no idea what
you're being accused of.

00:09:01.480 --> 00:09:03.400 align:middle line:90%
Your attorney, who--

00:09:03.400 --> 00:09:06.290 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: The state-- people
don't understand the Patriot

00:09:06.290 --> 00:09:06.980 align:middle line:90%
Act.

00:09:06.980 --> 00:09:09.290 align:middle line:84%
People think the
Patriot Act only

00:09:09.290 --> 00:09:13.490 align:middle line:84%
applies to foreign surveillance
of international telephone

00:09:13.490 --> 00:09:14.360 align:middle line:90%
calls.

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:16.810 align:middle line:90%
That is nonsense.

00:09:16.810 --> 00:09:19.910 align:middle line:84%
The Patriot Act is
7,000 pages modeled

00:09:19.910 --> 00:09:24.030 align:middle line:84%
on the Soviet
criminal code of 1926

00:09:24.030 --> 00:09:27.510 align:middle line:84%
that set up the KGB
and the gulag system.

00:09:27.510 --> 00:09:31.260 align:middle line:90%
And it relies on secret charges.

00:09:31.260 --> 00:09:32.750 align:middle line:90%
Think about this.

00:09:32.750 --> 00:09:39.240 align:middle line:84%
Secret charges, secret evidence,
secret grand jury testimony.

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:44.050 align:middle line:84%
You are never allowed to
know who has accused you--

00:09:44.050 --> 00:09:45.000 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Of what.

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.170 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: --of what.

00:09:46.170 --> 00:09:47.280 align:middle line:90%
What did I do?

00:09:47.280 --> 00:09:49.270 align:middle line:90%
Oh, I don't have to tell you.

00:09:49.270 --> 00:09:51.760 align:middle line:90%
You already know.

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:54.380 align:middle line:84%
You'd think it's
like a bad parent.

00:09:54.380 --> 00:09:56.304 align:middle line:90%
What did I do wrong, mommy?

00:09:56.304 --> 00:09:58.220 align:middle line:84%
You know, you already
know what you did wrong.

00:09:58.220 --> 00:09:59.590 align:middle line:90%
I don't have to tell you.

00:09:59.590 --> 00:10:00.430 align:middle line:90%
Oh, come on.

00:10:00.430 --> 00:10:03.060 align:middle line:84%
If you're going to send
me to prison for 25 years,

00:10:03.060 --> 00:10:04.730 align:middle line:90%
you do have to tell me.

00:10:04.730 --> 00:10:06.920 align:middle line:84%
And they're like,
not anymore we don't.

00:10:06.920 --> 00:10:09.730 align:middle line:90%
This is really scary stuff.

00:10:09.730 --> 00:10:11.800 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But did they
tell your attorney?

00:10:11.800 --> 00:10:12.550 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: Well--

00:10:12.550 --> 00:10:14.910 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Does the
attorney have the right

00:10:14.910 --> 00:10:17.260 align:middle line:84%
to know of the secret
charges and secret evidence?

00:10:17.260 --> 00:10:19.630 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: This is a
very important question,

00:10:19.630 --> 00:10:25.650 align:middle line:84%
and it's-- the attorney is
allowed to file for a security

00:10:25.650 --> 00:10:27.080 align:middle line:90%
clearance.

00:10:27.080 --> 00:10:29.949 align:middle line:84%
And the attorney is allowed,
after receiving a security

00:10:29.949 --> 00:10:32.240 align:middle line:84%
clearance, and some may have
a high security clearance,

00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:34.390 align:middle line:84%
some may have a low
security clearance,

00:10:34.390 --> 00:10:37.260 align:middle line:84%
depending on the
degree, they're allowed

00:10:37.260 --> 00:10:39.410 align:middle line:90%
to receive some information.

00:10:39.410 --> 00:10:43.610 align:middle line:84%
However, they are required
to sign a document stating

00:10:43.610 --> 00:10:48.290 align:middle line:84%
that they will never release
any information to the defendant

00:10:48.290 --> 00:10:53.650 align:middle line:84%
on pain of disbarment
from the legal profession,

00:10:53.650 --> 00:10:56.887 align:middle line:84%
financial sanction, or
even criminal prosecution

00:10:56.887 --> 00:10:57.386 align:middle line:90%
themselves.

00:10:57.386 --> 00:10:59.400 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I mean,
this is unbelievable.

00:10:59.400 --> 00:11:02.890 align:middle line:84%
You don't know why you're
arrested, you were never told.

00:11:02.890 --> 00:11:05.320 align:middle line:84%
You never were privy
to any of the evidence.

00:11:05.320 --> 00:11:08.690 align:middle line:84%
And not only that,
you're inept attorney,

00:11:08.690 --> 00:11:09.960 align:middle line:90%
inept might be a kind word.

00:11:09.960 --> 00:11:11.543 align:middle line:84%
It might be there
was collusion there.

00:11:11.543 --> 00:11:13.417 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: He was
absolutely in collusion.

00:11:13.417 --> 00:11:14.500 align:middle line:90%
What happened in my case--

00:11:14.500 --> 00:11:16.958 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And he was only given
maybe a small portion of it

00:11:16.958 --> 00:11:17.630 align:middle line:90%
himself.

00:11:17.630 --> 00:11:18.980 align:middle line:84%
Not that it would have
mattered because they

00:11:18.980 --> 00:11:20.396 align:middle line:84%
were going to nail
you either way.

00:11:20.396 --> 00:11:22.700 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: Well, what
happened was after my case was

00:11:22.700 --> 00:11:28.360 align:middle line:84%
dismissed, my first
attorney, Sam Talkin,

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:31.240 align:middle line:84%
who we called Sam No Talkin
because he refused to defend

00:11:31.240 --> 00:11:36.780 align:middle line:84%
me, finally handed over legal
documents to the attorney who

00:11:36.780 --> 00:11:39.311 align:middle line:84%
replaced him, Brian Shaughnessy,
who was one of the top

00:11:39.311 --> 00:11:39.810 align:middle line:90%
attorneys--

00:11:39.810 --> 00:11:40.440 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Who was
a real attorney.

00:11:40.440 --> 00:11:41.939 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: Who was
a real attorney,

00:11:41.939 --> 00:11:44.530 align:middle line:84%
one of the top attorneys in
Washington, great attorney,

00:11:44.530 --> 00:11:46.710 align:middle line:90%
now retired.

00:11:46.710 --> 00:11:51.100 align:middle line:84%
And we found in that a
non-disclosure agreement.

00:11:51.100 --> 00:11:54.010 align:middle line:84%
Three weeks after the
non-disclosure agreement,

00:11:54.010 --> 00:11:57.210 align:middle line:84%
I was declared incompetent
to stand trial.

00:11:57.210 --> 00:11:59.820 align:middle line:84%
And I was never allowed
to know that there

00:11:59.820 --> 00:12:04.400 align:middle line:84%
had been a secret debriefing
at the Justice Department.

00:12:04.400 --> 00:12:08.190 align:middle line:84%
I was declared incompetent
on the basis of my belief

00:12:08.190 --> 00:12:09.410 align:middle line:90%
in my innocence.

00:12:09.410 --> 00:12:12.110 align:middle line:84%
I continued to be
free and I continued

00:12:12.110 --> 00:12:19.990 align:middle line:84%
to demand a trial right up until
I was hauled into court one

00:12:19.990 --> 00:12:24.090 align:middle line:84%
day in September and
two things had happened.

00:12:24.090 --> 00:12:26.660 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Give us the dates
on the chronology of events.

00:12:26.660 --> 00:12:27.910 align:middle line:90%
You were arrested on what day?

00:12:27.910 --> 00:12:31.740 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: I was arrested
in March 11, 2004.

00:12:31.740 --> 00:12:32.670 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:12:32.670 --> 00:12:38.410 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: I was on bail
until September 23, 2005.

00:12:38.410 --> 00:12:39.200 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:12:39.200 --> 00:12:40.640 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: 18 months.

00:12:40.640 --> 00:12:41.970 align:middle line:90%
No court dates.

00:12:41.970 --> 00:12:42.950 align:middle line:90%
Nothing.

00:12:42.950 --> 00:12:43.890 align:middle line:90%
No action on my case--

00:12:43.890 --> 00:12:45.130 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: For a terrorist.

00:12:45.130 --> 00:12:47.588 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: --for a year and
a half with no court meetings.

00:12:47.588 --> 00:12:49.530 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: For an Iraqi agent?

00:12:49.530 --> 00:12:52.140 align:middle line:90%
For a traitor?

00:12:52.140 --> 00:12:53.090 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: No court.

00:12:53.090 --> 00:12:56.130 align:middle line:84%
All they wanted was to keep
me out of the election.

00:12:56.130 --> 00:12:57.630 align:middle line:84%
They wanted to get
me out of the way

00:12:57.630 --> 00:13:00.880 align:middle line:84%
because George Bush was running
for office against John Kerry.

00:13:00.880 --> 00:13:04.440 align:middle line:84%
It was a ferocious
election fight,

00:13:04.440 --> 00:13:07.940 align:middle line:84%
and George Bush knew that if
the American people discovered

00:13:07.940 --> 00:13:10.270 align:middle line:84%
the we gave advance
warnings about 9/11

00:13:10.270 --> 00:13:12.880 align:middle line:84%
and there was a peace option
on the table with Iraq,

00:13:12.880 --> 00:13:14.650 align:middle line:90%
he never had a chance.

00:13:14.650 --> 00:13:18.530 align:middle line:84%
So he was a dirty, ugly,
corrupt, selfish, weak

00:13:18.530 --> 00:13:19.710 align:middle line:90%
politician.

00:13:19.710 --> 00:13:23.064 align:middle line:84%
Very, very selfish, very,
very dangerous in my opinion.

00:13:23.064 --> 00:13:23.730 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:13:23.730 --> 00:13:26.303 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER:
Anti-American to do this.

00:13:26.303 --> 00:13:27.290 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:13:27.290 --> 00:13:29.480 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: But then
two things happened

00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:33.420 align:middle line:84%
in September, which forced
the Republicans' hand.

00:13:33.420 --> 00:13:37.620 align:middle line:84%
Colin Powell decided that he
was going to go on a book tour

00:13:37.620 --> 00:13:40.070 align:middle line:84%
to redeem his
reputation and to lay

00:13:40.070 --> 00:13:43.040 align:middle line:84%
the blame on the
assets at the CIA

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:47.320 align:middle line:84%
for not telling him
that Iraqi exiles had

00:13:47.320 --> 00:13:49.720 align:middle line:90%
lied about their intelligence.

00:13:49.720 --> 00:13:52.250 align:middle line:84%
And you can see
from my book that I

00:13:52.250 --> 00:13:55.000 align:middle line:84%
was one of the people
who did warn him.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:57.600 align:middle line:84%
He gave an interview
with Barbara Walters

00:13:57.600 --> 00:14:00.040 align:middle line:90%
on September 8th.

00:14:00.040 --> 00:14:03.670 align:middle line:84%
And on September 17th,
the Justice Department

00:14:03.670 --> 00:14:06.790 align:middle line:84%
rubber-stamped the
decision that I

00:14:06.790 --> 00:14:08.440 align:middle line:84%
should be sent to
Carswell Prison.

00:14:08.440 --> 00:14:10.370 align:middle line:90%
We know this from court papers.

00:14:10.370 --> 00:14:14.240 align:middle line:84%
On September 23rd, I
was hauled into court.

00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:17.030 align:middle line:84%
I was told by my
attorney that he

00:14:17.030 --> 00:14:20.800 align:middle line:84%
had no idea why I was
going into court that day.

00:14:20.800 --> 00:14:23.140 align:middle line:84%
He said, I think the
judge is just tired

00:14:23.140 --> 00:14:25.790 align:middle line:84%
and wants to know what's
happening in your case.

00:14:25.790 --> 00:14:31.180 align:middle line:84%
And he'd like us to try
to solve this thing.

00:14:31.180 --> 00:14:34.200 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, he'd like us to
try to solve this thing.

00:14:34.200 --> 00:14:39.140 align:middle line:84%
And my uncle, who is an
attorney, Ted Lindauer,

00:14:39.140 --> 00:14:42.970 align:middle line:84%
wonderful attorney, 40 years in
the University of Chicago Law

00:14:42.970 --> 00:14:45.320 align:middle line:84%
School, a real fighter,
a Lindauer thing.

00:14:45.320 --> 00:14:47.180 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: The
Lindauer thing, yeah.

00:14:47.180 --> 00:14:49.270 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: He flew out
to New York to meet me.

00:14:49.270 --> 00:14:50.728 align:middle line:84%
He said, something's
going on here.

00:14:50.728 --> 00:14:52.300 align:middle line:90%
Something's wrong.

00:14:52.300 --> 00:14:55.730 align:middle line:84%
And we both knew that something
was going to happen that day.

00:14:55.730 --> 00:14:57.700 align:middle line:84%
At that point, I
had not been allowed

00:14:57.700 --> 00:15:00.340 align:middle line:84%
to see the psychiatric
evaluations.

00:15:00.340 --> 00:15:05.020 align:middle line:84%
I showed up in court
and right before court,

00:15:05.020 --> 00:15:07.790 align:middle line:84%
my attorney insisted right
until the last minute

00:15:07.790 --> 00:15:10.210 align:middle line:90%
he had no idea why I was there.

00:15:10.210 --> 00:15:14.420 align:middle line:84%
And we get into court and
he says, oh, surprise.

00:15:14.420 --> 00:15:17.916 align:middle line:84%
They've decided they're
going to send you to prison.

00:15:17.916 --> 00:15:19.290 align:middle line:84%
They've decided
that you're going

00:15:19.290 --> 00:15:22.930 align:middle line:84%
to be declared incompetent
to stand trial,

00:15:22.930 --> 00:15:26.100 align:middle line:84%
and we're going to be send you
to prison on Carswell Air Force

00:15:26.100 --> 00:15:26.969 align:middle line:90%
Base.

00:15:26.969 --> 00:15:27.760 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: In Texas.

00:15:27.760 --> 00:15:28.940 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: In Texas.

00:15:28.940 --> 00:15:35.600 align:middle line:84%
For a in prison-- this is not
a hospital, this is a prison.

00:15:35.600 --> 00:15:38.760 align:middle line:84%
And it's a prison on
a military base, which

00:15:38.760 --> 00:15:43.100 align:middle line:84%
is in the middle of a
war that they are losing.

00:15:43.100 --> 00:15:46.010 align:middle line:84%
These men have
friends who are dying.

00:15:46.010 --> 00:15:49.310 align:middle line:84%
They have men-- they have family
members, they have brothers,

00:15:49.310 --> 00:15:53.530 align:middle line:84%
they have their neighbors who
are out there shedding blood

00:15:53.530 --> 00:15:56.250 align:middle line:84%
in Iraq, who are getting
blown up in Iraq,

00:15:56.250 --> 00:16:01.090 align:middle line:84%
and you're telling them that
this Iraqi agent is going

00:16:01.090 --> 00:16:02.710 align:middle line:84%
to be housed on
their military base.

00:16:02.710 --> 00:16:04.126 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And
that's what you were

00:16:04.126 --> 00:16:05.740 align:middle line:84%
known as in prison,
the Iraqi agent.

00:16:05.740 --> 00:16:07.074 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: The Iraqi agent.

00:16:07.074 --> 00:16:08.490 align:middle line:84%
And as far as they
were concerned,

00:16:08.490 --> 00:16:11.434 align:middle line:84%
that probably meant
I was an Iraqi spy.

00:16:11.434 --> 00:16:12.850 align:middle line:84%
But as far as they
were concerned,

00:16:12.850 --> 00:16:14.487 align:middle line:90%
I was the ultimate traitor--

00:16:14.487 --> 00:16:15.070 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Sure

00:16:15.070 --> 00:16:16.710 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: --to America.

00:16:16.710 --> 00:16:19.270 align:middle line:84%
They didn't know that
I'd warned about 9/11.

00:16:19.270 --> 00:16:23.510 align:middle line:84%
They didn't know that I tried
to save their lives by trying

00:16:23.510 --> 00:16:25.470 align:middle line:84%
to tell Congress
not to go to war,

00:16:25.470 --> 00:16:26.970 align:middle line:84%
because we didn't
need to go to war.

00:16:26.970 --> 00:16:27.850 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:16:27.850 --> 00:16:29.058 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: They had no idea.

00:16:29.058 --> 00:16:32.180 align:middle line:84%
All they knew was that
this traitorous spy

00:16:32.180 --> 00:16:34.820 align:middle line:84%
was being locked
up on their base.

00:16:34.820 --> 00:16:40.220 align:middle line:84%
And my life became-- anyway,
so I go into the courtroom

00:16:40.220 --> 00:16:42.780 align:middle line:84%
and I have not been
warned anything.

00:16:42.780 --> 00:16:45.230 align:middle line:90%
I had no idea what was coming.

00:16:45.230 --> 00:16:48.225 align:middle line:84%
And they threw the paper down
on the desk and we looked at it,

00:16:48.225 --> 00:16:51.530 align:middle line:90%
and I was like, holy God, what?

00:16:51.530 --> 00:16:52.170 align:middle line:90%
What is this?

00:16:52.170 --> 00:16:55.570 align:middle line:84%
And my life flashed
in front of my eyes.

00:16:55.570 --> 00:16:57.390 align:middle line:84%
And all of the good
things that I'd

00:16:57.390 --> 00:16:59.420 align:middle line:84%
done, all of the hard
work that I'd done

00:16:59.420 --> 00:17:03.790 align:middle line:84%
was erased by these
irresponsible nutcase

00:17:03.790 --> 00:17:04.874 align:middle line:90%
psychology people--

00:17:04.874 --> 00:17:05.540 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:17:05.540 --> 00:17:07.790 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: -who wanted
to say that psychology

00:17:07.790 --> 00:17:10.060 align:middle line:90%
decides reality.

00:17:10.060 --> 00:17:10.937 align:middle line:90%
Talk about--

00:17:10.937 --> 00:17:13.020 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Instead of
external evidence and events?

00:17:13.020 --> 00:17:15.430 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: Instead of
external evidence and events.

00:17:15.430 --> 00:17:18.190 align:middle line:84%
And they felt that because
they were psychology people,

00:17:18.190 --> 00:17:20.849 align:middle line:84%
they could eradicate
anything that

00:17:20.849 --> 00:17:22.669 align:middle line:84%
got in the way of
their diagnosis.

00:17:22.669 --> 00:17:23.960 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: But their diagnosis--

00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:25.050 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: Very frightening.

00:17:25.050 --> 00:17:26.591 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But this
was actually only,

00:17:26.591 --> 00:17:28.760 align:middle line:84%
they were shills
playing out an agenda.

00:17:28.760 --> 00:17:31.410 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: They were shills
playing out an agenda.

00:17:31.410 --> 00:17:33.870 align:middle line:84%
They were prostituting
themselves

00:17:33.870 --> 00:17:36.214 align:middle line:84%
to corrupt politicians
in Washington.

00:17:36.214 --> 00:17:36.880 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:17:36.880 --> 00:17:39.296 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: And they knew very
well that I wanted a trial.

00:17:39.296 --> 00:17:42.610 align:middle line:84%
I had very little sympathy,
to be perfectly honest,

00:17:42.610 --> 00:17:43.950 align:middle line:90%
with psychology.

00:17:43.950 --> 00:17:47.880 align:middle line:84%
I do not believe that psychology
belongs in the courtroom

00:17:47.880 --> 00:17:51.055 align:middle line:84%
unless you are a very
severe schizophrenic,

00:17:51.055 --> 00:17:56.080 align:middle line:84%
or you have been abused, like
if you're an abused child

00:17:56.080 --> 00:17:59.120 align:middle line:84%
or abused woman who
has like a reason,

00:17:59.120 --> 00:18:02.020 align:middle line:84%
like you're striking back
at an abusive relationship.

00:18:02.020 --> 00:18:06.826 align:middle line:84%
I don't want to hear that
you have manic depression

00:18:06.826 --> 00:18:08.200 align:middle line:84%
and, therefore,
you're not taking

00:18:08.200 --> 00:18:10.650 align:middle line:84%
responsibility for
identity theft.

00:18:10.650 --> 00:18:15.470 align:middle line:84%
Or you're an embezzler
and oh, I can't help it.

00:18:15.470 --> 00:18:17.940 align:middle line:84%
I can't be held
responsible for my actions.

00:18:17.940 --> 00:18:18.890 align:middle line:90%
Garbage.

00:18:18.890 --> 00:18:21.720 align:middle line:84%
You most-- I would have no
sympathy for those people.

00:18:21.720 --> 00:18:24.790 align:middle line:84%
And, in fact, the FBI
agent who arrested me later

00:18:24.790 --> 00:18:27.170 align:middle line:84%
told me that he considered me
one of the most outstanding

00:18:27.170 --> 00:18:29.140 align:middle line:84%
defendants that he'd
ever seen because I

00:18:29.140 --> 00:18:31.240 align:middle line:90%
refused to play that game.

00:18:31.240 --> 00:18:34.360 align:middle line:84%
And they were actually
impressed because most people

00:18:34.360 --> 00:18:36.680 align:middle line:84%
in the justice system,
most defendants

00:18:36.680 --> 00:18:38.870 align:middle line:84%
will take a
psychiatric diagnosis

00:18:38.870 --> 00:18:42.569 align:middle line:84%
as they're like, ha, ha, I
escaped, I beat the system.

00:18:42.569 --> 00:18:43.110 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: No.

00:18:43.110 --> 00:18:44.430 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: And I
was like oh, no.

00:18:44.430 --> 00:18:46.263 align:middle line:84%
If you think you've got
evidence against me,

00:18:46.263 --> 00:18:49.126 align:middle line:84%
you have every
right to convict me.

00:18:49.126 --> 00:18:50.750 align:middle line:84%
You have the right
to sentence me and I

00:18:50.750 --> 00:18:52.208 align:middle line:84%
better take
responsibility for what

00:18:52.208 --> 00:18:55.514 align:middle line:84%
I did, but I have every
right to challenge--

00:18:55.514 --> 00:18:56.430 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Stand trial.

00:18:56.430 --> 00:18:59.080 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: -stand trial and
challenge the accusations

