00:20:10.440 --> 00:20:11.950 align:middle line:90%
The law very clearly says--

00:20:11.950 --> 00:20:13.700 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: They wanted to
make sure Sam Talkin stayed

00:20:13.700 --> 00:20:15.199 align:middle line:84%
in that position
of ineffectiveness.

00:20:15.199 --> 00:20:16.320 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: Absolutely.

00:20:16.320 --> 00:20:19.710 align:middle line:84%
They knew indifferent,
ineffective counsel.

00:20:19.710 --> 00:20:21.090 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK, now what happens?

00:20:21.090 --> 00:20:23.110 align:middle line:84%
So you're there in court
and you find this out.

00:20:23.110 --> 00:20:24.568 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: I was
given-- they said

00:20:24.568 --> 00:20:27.720 align:middle line:84%
that if I would agree to
self-surrender to prison,

00:20:27.720 --> 00:20:30.910 align:middle line:84%
I would have 10 days to
get my affairs in order.

00:20:30.910 --> 00:20:33.680 align:middle line:84%
Now I had not been
told that I might

00:20:33.680 --> 00:20:37.280 align:middle line:84%
be going to prison that day, so
I had not made any arrangements

00:20:37.280 --> 00:20:42.220 align:middle line:84%
for my home, my pets, my
family, my friends, you know.

00:20:42.220 --> 00:20:46.970 align:middle line:84%
I was horrified, terrorized
by the whole thing,

00:20:46.970 --> 00:20:49.630 align:middle line:84%
but I had no choice but to
give them what they wanted.

00:20:49.630 --> 00:20:52.090 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, I would
have been lost.

00:20:52.090 --> 00:20:57.082 align:middle line:84%
My uncle was like, OK, try
not to yell at the judge.

00:20:57.082 --> 00:20:58.540 align:middle line:84%
They were afraid
I was really going

00:20:58.540 --> 00:20:59.750 align:middle line:90%
to start screaming in court.

00:20:59.750 --> 00:21:01.500 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, you,
your family is known.

00:21:01.500 --> 00:21:03.460 align:middle line:84%
You're scrappers and
fighters, and you'll

00:21:03.460 --> 00:21:04.670 align:middle line:90%
say what's on your mind.

00:21:04.670 --> 00:21:05.000 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:06.090 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: You don't
mince any words.

00:21:06.090 --> 00:21:07.673 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And I don't
mince any words.

00:21:07.673 --> 00:21:11.290 align:middle line:84%
And if you're talking about,
you know-- I'm an asset.

00:21:11.290 --> 00:21:14.840 align:middle line:84%
If they can do this to
me and I know my rights

00:21:14.840 --> 00:21:20.140 align:middle line:84%
under the Constitution, I
know my historical rights.

00:21:20.140 --> 00:21:24.700 align:middle line:84%
OK, I am a highly-educated
white female.

00:21:24.700 --> 00:21:30.240 align:middle line:84%
I am not an inner city
youth drug addict.

00:21:30.240 --> 00:21:33.720 align:middle line:84%
I'm not a criminal, an
illiterate criminal.

00:21:33.720 --> 00:21:36.245 align:middle line:84%
You know, I have
a Master's degree

00:21:36.245 --> 00:21:37.745 align:middle line:84%
from the London
School of Economics.

00:21:37.745 --> 00:21:40.810 align:middle line:90%


00:21:40.810 --> 00:21:44.070 align:middle line:84%
My family has run this
country for hundreds of years.

00:21:44.070 --> 00:21:45.445 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah,
been in politics.

00:21:45.445 --> 00:21:46.780 align:middle line:90%
>>LINDAUER: Been in politics.

00:21:46.780 --> 00:21:50.840 align:middle line:84%
I mean, they go way
back, way, way back.

00:21:50.840 --> 00:21:53.062 align:middle line:84%
Then again, you can find
six degrees of separation

00:21:53.062 --> 00:21:55.020 align:middle line:84%
for any family, I think,
in America these days.

00:21:55.020 --> 00:21:56.145 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, that's true.

00:21:56.145 --> 00:22:01.260 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: But the point is is
that if they can do this to me,

00:22:01.260 --> 00:22:04.840 align:middle line:84%
and I'm a fighter, I'm an
advocate, I'm an activist,

00:22:04.840 --> 00:22:07.220 align:middle line:84%
then what are they going
to do to somebody else who

00:22:07.220 --> 00:22:11.412 align:middle line:84%
doesn't have my skill at
beating, like an asset--

00:22:11.412 --> 00:22:12.870 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Your
skill and knowledge,

00:22:12.870 --> 00:22:15.370 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: My skill and
knowledge running a blockade.

00:22:15.370 --> 00:22:20.045 align:middle line:84%
An asset is trained to take
any circumstances that come

00:22:20.045 --> 00:22:23.230 align:middle line:84%
and to beat it and
run the blockade.

00:22:23.230 --> 00:22:24.530 align:middle line:90%
That's what we do.

00:22:24.530 --> 00:22:27.730 align:middle line:84%
We don't go in when it's
easy; we go in it's hard.

00:22:27.730 --> 00:22:30.990 align:middle line:84%
And I'm telling you, if
they can do this to me

00:22:30.990 --> 00:22:35.360 align:middle line:84%
then the rest of you
are in serious trouble.

00:22:35.360 --> 00:22:39.610 align:middle line:84%
So anyway, I went--
but I had no choice.

00:22:39.610 --> 00:22:42.360 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So you got someone
to take care of your dogs.

00:22:42.360 --> 00:22:46.200 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: I went
home that night.

00:22:46.200 --> 00:22:48.240 align:middle line:84%
I had 10 days to get
my affairs in order.

00:22:48.240 --> 00:22:52.446 align:middle line:84%
I self-surrendered to
Carswell Air Force Base.

00:22:52.446 --> 00:22:53.820 align:middle line:84%
The first thing
they said to me--

00:22:53.820 --> 00:22:55.320 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Did they
pay your airfare?

00:22:55.320 --> 00:22:57.810 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: The
US Marshals, yes.

00:22:57.810 --> 00:22:58.500 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:22:58.500 --> 00:23:02.020 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: But when I got
to Carswell Air Force Base,

00:23:02.020 --> 00:23:05.180 align:middle line:84%
they did an intake
psych evaluation

00:23:05.180 --> 00:23:07.750 align:middle line:84%
like just when you first come
in and they talk to you for 15

00:23:07.750 --> 00:23:12.050 align:middle line:84%
minutes, and they said the guy--
they have a real psychiatrist,

00:23:12.050 --> 00:23:17.410 align:middle line:84%
who is trained to reject
incompetence defenses,

00:23:17.410 --> 00:23:20.402 align:middle line:84%
and trained to--
the government-- you

00:23:20.402 --> 00:23:21.610 align:middle line:90%
have to understand something.

00:23:21.610 --> 00:23:25.914 align:middle line:84%
Ordinarily, a government, a
Justice Department hates this.

00:23:25.914 --> 00:23:26.580 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:23:26.580 --> 00:23:27.910 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: A
Justice Department--

00:23:27.910 --> 00:23:28.970 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: They want
you to stand trial.

00:23:28.970 --> 00:23:30.719 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: -they want
you to stand trial.

00:23:30.719 --> 00:23:32.310 align:middle line:84%
They want to-- as
my second attorney,

00:23:32.310 --> 00:23:35.500 align:middle line:84%
Brian Shaughnessy
said-- he was one

00:23:35.500 --> 00:23:38.750 align:middle line:84%
of the chief prosecutors in
the court of Judge Sirica.

00:23:38.750 --> 00:23:41.800 align:middle line:84%
Judge Sirica, Maximum John
is what they called him.

00:23:41.800 --> 00:23:44.080 align:middle line:84%
He sentenced people to
huge sentences, he's like,

00:23:44.080 --> 00:23:45.310 align:middle line:90%
bring me people to convict.

00:23:45.310 --> 00:23:47.020 align:middle line:90%
I want to send them to jail.

00:23:47.020 --> 00:23:50.475 align:middle line:84%
Brian used to say, Susan, I
would be even madder than hell

00:23:50.475 --> 00:23:53.032 align:middle line:84%
if you were declared
incompetent.

00:23:53.032 --> 00:23:54.990 align:middle line:84%
He said, I would have
wanted you to stand trial

00:23:54.990 --> 00:23:56.450 align:middle line:90%
so I could send you to prison.

00:23:56.450 --> 00:23:59.620 align:middle line:84%
He said, this is outrageous that
they said you were incompetent.

00:23:59.620 --> 00:24:01.930 align:middle line:84%
He said, this is an offense
against our legal system

00:24:01.930 --> 00:24:03.800 align:middle line:84%
that they said you
are incompetent.

00:24:03.800 --> 00:24:08.240 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So the first
psychiatrist to evaluate you,

00:24:08.240 --> 00:24:10.410 align:middle line:84%
his job is to
basically declare you

00:24:10.410 --> 00:24:14.240 align:middle line:84%
are competent to stand trial,
that's standard procedure.

00:24:14.240 --> 00:24:16.589 align:middle line:10%
>>LINDAUER: And so the
prison psychiatrist

00:24:16.589 --> 00:24:18.130 align:middle line:10%
took one look at me
and said, well, I

00:24:18.130 --> 00:24:21.980 align:middle line:10%
can tell right now that these
reports about you are garbage.

00:24:21.980 --> 00:24:26.220 align:middle line:10%
He said, real people who are
incompetent are hallucinating.

00:24:26.220 --> 00:24:29.640 align:middle line:84%
They don't-- they see
something that isn't there.

00:24:29.640 --> 00:24:31.830 align:middle line:90%
They're hearing voices.

00:24:31.830 --> 00:24:34.150 align:middle line:90%
You don't have any depression.

00:24:34.150 --> 00:24:35.720 align:middle line:90%
You're not weeping hysterically.

00:24:35.720 --> 00:24:37.050 align:middle line:90%
You're not out of control.

00:24:37.050 --> 00:24:38.750 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You're pretty
pissed off at this point.

00:24:38.750 --> 00:24:40.750 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: I'm pretty
pissed off at this point,

00:24:40.750 --> 00:24:42.130 align:middle line:84%
but I was under
control because I

00:24:42.130 --> 00:24:44.742 align:middle line:84%
was afraid of being belligerent
and like, you know, hitting.

00:24:44.742 --> 00:24:46.700 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, you had
to try to keep it down.

00:24:46.700 --> 00:24:48.366 align:middle line:84%
>>LINDAUER: I had to
be very controlled,

00:24:48.366 --> 00:24:52.150 align:middle line:84%
had to be very
controlled at all times.

00:24:52.150 --> 00:24:52.670 align:middle line:90%
And I was.

00:24:52.670 --> 00:24:57.170 align:middle line:84%
I was exercising-- I was in
a state of terrible shock.

00:24:57.170 --> 00:24:59.360 align:middle line:84%
And he said, I can
tell right now,

00:24:59.360 --> 00:25:01.230 align:middle line:84%
he said, this is your
attorney's doing.

00:25:01.230 --> 00:25:03.730 align:middle line:84%
He said, sometimes
attorneys when

00:25:03.730 --> 00:25:07.710 align:middle line:84%
